: "2022", "bbox": [463.8, 928.2, 501.3, 947.0]}, {"text": "1,320", "bbox": [769.7, 928.2, 811.9, 947.0]}, {"text": "2023", "bbox": [463.8, 959.5, 501.3, 978.2]}, {"text": "2,403", "bbox": [769.7, 959.5, 811.9, 978.2]}, {"text": "Commercial Paper", "bbox": [153.2, 1011.8, 321.9, 1032.6]}, {"text": "On February 26, 2016, we established a commercial paper program that allows us to have a maximum of", "bbox": [153.2, 1066.1, 1103.7, 1086.9]}, {"text": "$2 billion in commercial paper outstanding, with maturities up to 397 days from the date of issuance. We do not", "bbox": [153.2, 1091.1, 1103.7, 1111.9]}, {"text": "intend to have outstanding commercial paper borrowings in excess of available capacity under our bank", "bbox": [153.2, 1116.1, 1103.8, 1136.9]}, {"text": "revolving credit facilities. During 2018, we had no borrowings or repayments under the commercial paper", "bbox": [153.2, 1141.1, 1103.7, 1161.9]}, {"text": "program. At December 31, 2018, we had no amounts outstanding under the commercial paper program.", "bbox": [153.2, 1166.1, 1019.2, 1186.9]}, {"text": "MPC Revolving Credit Agreements", "bbox": [153.2, 1220.0, 469.9, 1240.8]}, {"text": "On August 28, 2018, we entered into credit agreements with a syndicate of lenders to replace MPC’s previous", "bbox": [153.2, 1274.3, 1103.7, 1295.1]}, {"text": "five-year $2.5 billion bank revolving credit facility due in 2022 and our previous 364-day $1 billion bank", "bbox": [153.2, 1299.3, 1103.8, 1320.1]}, {"text": "revolving agreement that expired in July 2018. The new credit agreements, which became effective October 1,", "bbox": [153.2, 1324.3, 1103.8, 1345.1]}, {"text": "2018 in connection with the Andeavor acquisition, provide for a $5 billion five-year revolving credit agreement", "bbox": [153.2, 1349.3, 1103.6, 1370.1]}, {"text": "that expires in 2023 (“new MPC five-year credit agreement”) and a $1 billion 364-day revolving credit", "bbox": [153.2, 1374.3, 1103.6, 1395.2]}, {"text": "agreement that expires in 2019 (“new MPC 364-day credit agreement” and together with the new MPC five-year", "bbox": [153.2, 1399.3, 1103.6, 1420.2]}, {"text": "credit agreement, the “new MPC credit agreements”).", "bbox": [153.2, 1424.3, 601.8, 1445.2]}, {"text": "157", "bbox": [612.9, 1475.4, 644.1, 1496.2]}]}